Interface PhoneListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
TestPhone, PhoneModel
public interface PhoneListener

This describes the non-command events that a phone may respond to. So, when a phone is added to a call, the phone will be notified using this interface. Creation date: (2000-02-09 12:22:50)
